title: Pregnant Irina Shayk Takes Driver's Ed Lessons in Los Angeles – See the Pic!
text: Pregnant Irina Shayk Takes Driver's Ed Lessons in Los Angeles – See the Pic! by Zach Seemayer 7:52 PM PST, January 31, 2017 Photo: Getty Images With a baby on the way , Irina Shayk has decided it's time to learn how to drive. The Victoria's Secret model, who is pregnant with her first child with boyfriend Bradley Cooper , got behind the wheel of a fire engine red Toyota Corolla on Tuesday during her driving lesson in Los Angeles, California. Photo: AKM-GSI WATCH: Irina Shayk Shows Off Tiny Baby Bump at Victoria’s Secret After Party: Pics! The 30-year-old mom-to-be rocked an all-black ensemble -- including a pair of dark shades and a black beanie pulled down over her long brunette locks -- and a loose-fitting graphic tee, as she drove around the city. In December, Shayk began sporting an emerald-stone band on her left ring finger, which sparked engagement rumors between her and Cooper. While the couple hasn't commented on these rumors, the model was spotted wearing the same ring on that finger during her driving lesson. Shayk first showed off her burgeoning baby bump on the Victoria's Secret Fashion Show walkway in November. The Russian-born beauty did her best to conceal her growing belly, in a number of more covered-up looks throughout the night. Photo: Getty Images For more on her and Cooper's forthcoming bundle of joy , and the ongoing engagement rumors circling the cute couple, check out the video below. RELATED SLIDESHOW
